          "text": "set %complaint% = \u0022Compiler returned missing-actions for step %step.Index% (text: \u0027%step.Text%\u0027). Current action set is insufficient: %planStep.actions%. Reason: %!error.Message%. Return a corrected action set for step %step.Index% only. Include \u0060confidence\u0060 (VeryHigh|High|Medium|Low|VeryLow) and \u0060explanation\u0060 (one short sentence when confidence is Medium or below) \u2014 recovery confidence matters because it tells the dev whether even the correction is a guess.\u0022, type=string",
